      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — The preceding verse mentioned the lightning with its effects; this gives us the report of the thunder, and the increasing storm of hail and fire that attended it. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Yea, he sent out his arrows — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Namely, lightnings, as it is expressed in the next clause; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "and scattered them ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Namely, mine enemies, which is sufficiently understood from ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 18:3",
        "children": []
