        "class": "",
        "text": ", means adverbially \"in abundance,\" is the parallel to ויּשׁלח. It is generally taken, after the analogy of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 49:23",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", in the sense of בּרק, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
